      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COOL IT MISS (6) struggled for best form latest, finishing 5th (23.53) in a Grade 6 at this track. Has won here at this journey. Speedy beginner who can find the front despite the tricky draw. Can make amends. ZARA TURBO (1) comes off an average effort last start when fifth at Angle Park over 342m behind Specked (20.19) in a Grade 6. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Expected to run well. HERE COMES SHAKA (4) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Has been in the money the last three starts, the latest when third (20.16) at Angle Park. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. OUR LAURA ROSE (2) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can atone.",
